From: Mel Gorman <mgorman@suse.de>
Date: Mon, 31 Oct 2011 17:07:48 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] ext4: warn if direct reclaim tries to writeback pages

References: Page reclaim functionality
Patch-mainline: Yes (v3.2)
Git-commit: 966dbde2c208e07bab7a45a7855e1e693eabe661

Direct reclaim should never writeback pages.  Warn if an attempt is made.

